[chanting]: Sashi pukyi

04:12.600 --> 04:14.732
jukshing metok tram,

04:14.776 --> 04:18.301
Sashi pukyi jukshing
metok tram.

04:18.345 --> 04:21.957
Sashi pukyi
jukshing metok tram.

04:22.000 --> 04:23.741
Sashi pukyi...

