Hey!

04:57.862 --> 04:58.820
Nothing.

04:58.863 --> 05:00.082
Hey, sorry.

05:00.125 --> 05:02.127
What is it?Nothing. It's okay.

05:02.171 --> 05:03.520
Don't worry.No, I'm not worried.

05:03.564 --> 05:05.522
