05:05.566 --> 05:06.523
Let me see.

05:06.567 --> 05:08.569
It's a...
it's a mandala.

05:09.918 --> 05:12.616
They use it in, uh,
Kagyu Buddhism.

05:12.660 --> 05:14.488
I learned about it in Tibet.

05:15.532 --> 05:16.968
So you're...

05:17.012 --> 05:18.970
you're... a Buddhist now?No.

05:19.014 --> 05:21.016
No. I'm just, uh...

05:21.059 --> 05:23.497
I don't know, um...

05:23.540 --> 05:24.802
exploring.

05:24.846 --> 05:26.978
Okay.But don't worry,
I'm still me, so...

05:27.022 --> 05:29.198
No, I know you're still
you. I just, I mean,Yeah.

05:29.241 --> 05:31.983
I find it weird that you're
criticizing the Catholic stuff

05:32.027 --> 05:33.985
in my job, while
at yours...Oh, no. Oh, no.

05:34.029 --> 05:35.465
Buddhism's not a religion.

05:35.509 --> 05:37.380
It's-it's a practice.

05:37.424 --> 05:38.947
Okay.

05:38.990 --> 05:41.253
Well, I got to go.
They need me in court.Okay.

05:41.297 --> 05:42.603
Bye.Bye. Oh, hey, hey, hey.

05:42.646 --> 05:44.692
The Everest expedition's,
like, three months away,

05:44.735 --> 05:47.259
and there's a prep meeting
next week.Where is it?

05:47.303 --> 05:48.565
Denver.
So you got to decide

05:48.609 --> 05:50.524
if you want to lead the tour.Um...

05:50.567 --> 05:52.569
can we talk about this later?
I'm kind of running late.

05:52.613 --> 05:53.614
Oh, no, of course. Yeah, yeah.

05:53.657 --> 05:54.745
Okay.Okay.

05:54.789 --> 05:56.268
Oh, don't leave that
bowl of rice out.

05:56.312 --> 05:58.662
Birds eat it, and their
stomach explode.

06:00.185 --> 06:02.405
Really?

06:02.449 --> 06:03.972
[crow cawing]

06:04.015 --> 06:07.410
[children chattering
indistinctly]

06:07.454 --> 06:10.021
So, what is this?

06:10.065 --> 06:12.720
Just someone who needs
some spiritual advice.

06:12.763 --> 06:14.330
BEN:
What, like eating meat
on Fridays?

06:14.374 --> 06:15.636
DAVID:
No.

06:15.679 --> 06:17.638
She's just hearing
some kind of demon.

06:17.681 --> 06:18.900
Okay.

06:18.943 --> 06:21.729
All right, well, look,
uh, give me a call

06:21.772 --> 06:23.644
if there's actually
any real

06:23.687 --> 06:26.386
supernatural crap
to debunk.

06:26.429 --> 06:28.736
I'll pick you up
at 4:00. Go.

06:32.435 --> 06:33.654
Sonia?

06:33.697 --> 06:35.699
Yes. David.

06:35.743 --> 06:37.527
Thanks for coming.

06:37.571 --> 06:39.007
Just one moment.

06:46.797 --> 06:48.103
Oh. Please.

06:54.501 --> 06:55.719
Dwight Ferrell.

06:55.763 --> 06:57.765
EMA:
And where do you
currently reside?

06:57.808 --> 06:59.419
Rikers Island.

06:59.462 --> 07:01.682
Enhanced Supervision Unit Three.On November 10,

07:01.725 --> 07:04.554
2019, you were arrested
for the murder

07:04.598 --> 07:07.339
of three Hispanic youths.

07:07.383 --> 07:09.037
Later you confessed
to these killings.

07:09.080 --> 07:10.386
Is that correct?

07:10.430 --> 07:11.648
FERREL: Yes.EMA: Two weeks later,

07:11.692 --> 07:14.259
you confessed
to other murders as well.

07:15.696 --> 07:18.002
Yes.These were the three families
that Orson LeRoux

07:18.046 --> 07:19.787
has been convicted
of murdering.

07:19.830 --> 07:21.571
Yes.How did you kill

07:21.615 --> 07:24.008
these families,
Mr. Ferrell?

07:24.052 --> 07:25.575
FERRELL:
In New York,

07:25.619 --> 07:28.186
the easiest way to gain
access to a house

07:28.230 --> 07:30.667
is by attending
open houses.

07:30.711 --> 07:32.843
I would go
to Mr. LeRoux's showings,

07:32.887 --> 07:35.629
because he always had
large turnouts.

07:35.672 --> 07:37.195
I would go unnoticed,

07:37.239 --> 07:40.503
and then I
would hide--

07:40.547 --> 07:42.679
in closets,
children's playrooms,

07:42.723 --> 07:44.289
sometimes the attic--

07:44.333 --> 07:46.466
and I would wait.

07:47.554 --> 07:48.903
And then?

07:48.946 --> 07:50.600
FERRELL:
I would hurt them.

07:50.644 --> 07:52.036
EMA:
Kill them?

07:52.080 --> 07:53.777
FERRELL:
Yes.

07:53.821 --> 07:55.823
Starting with the father,
and then the mother.

07:55.866 --> 07:57.302
I saved the children

07:57.346 --> 07:58.739
for last.

07:58.782 --> 08:00.523
Why are you admitting
to this now,

08:00.567 --> 08:02.307
Mr. Ferrell?Because I'm looking

08:02.351 --> 08:03.526
for redemption.

08:03.570 --> 08:05.485
I don't want
to be responsible

08:05.528 --> 08:07.269
for somebody like Mr. LeRoux

08:07.312 --> 08:08.662
spending the rest
of his life

08:08.705 --> 08:10.925
in prison.

08:12.448 --> 08:13.710
[whispers]:
Mira.

08:13.754 --> 08:15.320
Hey.

08:15.364 --> 08:17.018
There's no way Dwight
killed those families.

08:17.061 --> 08:18.585
There's no shared M.O.

08:18.628 --> 08:20.761
Their forensic psychologist
saw a similar pattern.

08:20.804 --> 08:23.633
Yes, and that forensic
psychologist is Leland Townsend.

08:23.677 --> 08:25.592
Mira, don't help
the defense.

08:25.635 --> 08:28.290
LeRoux will be released,
and he will kill again.

08:30.684 --> 08:32.468
Thank you for coming, David.

08:32.512 --> 08:35.036
You do know I'm
not a priest?

08:35.079 --> 08:36.646
I do.

08:36.690 --> 08:38.779
I just need some advice.

08:38.822 --> 08:40.171
I hear a voice.

08:40.215 --> 08:42.783
It was quiet at first,
uh, nonverbal.

08:42.826 --> 08:44.611
Then it-it...

08:44.654 --> 08:45.916
it grew...

08:45.960 --> 08:48.484
into something
of a whisper.

08:48.528 --> 08:50.617
It's like Kings, chapter 19.

08:50.660 --> 08:52.793
"God's voice
was in the whisper"

08:52.836 --> 08:54.795
after the earthquake
and the fire.

08:54.838 --> 08:56.536
What'd the whisper say?

08:57.624 --> 08:59.626
It said to kill.

09:04.456 --> 09:07.459
That's not God's voice.

09:07.503 --> 09:09.679
God doesn't tell
people to kill.

09:09.723 --> 09:13.335
He told Saul kill them all.

09:13.378 --> 09:15.859
Amalek, and his men

09:15.903 --> 09:17.121
and his women,
his children,

09:17.165 --> 09:18.383
and all infants.

09:18.427 --> 09:20.472
That was the Old Testament.

09:20.516 --> 09:22.518
And why does that matter?

09:26.914 --> 09:28.480
Because...

09:28.524 --> 09:31.658
God needed to protect
his chosen ones.

09:31.701 --> 09:34.138
[teakettle whistling]

09:34.182 --> 09:35.705
[exhales]

09:39.753 --> 09:42.190
[whistling stops]And does he not
anymore?

09:43.800 --> 09:46.455
DAVID:
Not in the same way.

09:47.543 --> 09:49.719
The New Testament is different.

10:00.948 --> 10:02.950
[muffled shout in distance]

10:11.480 --> 10:13.482
[muffled shout]

10:15.919 --> 10:17.355
SONIA:
David.

10:25.189 --> 10:26.800
Forgive me.

10:28.628 --> 10:30.455
♪

10:50.214 --> 10:51.694
That's not good.

10:51.738 --> 10:53.391
