10:53.435 --> 10:56.046
You should call
the doctor.

10:56.090 --> 10:57.700
Go do your homework.
I got this.

10:57.744 --> 10:59.223
No, I'm here.MAN: Hello?

10:59.267 --> 11:01.791
Hello, Doctor?
Uh, Dr. Docker? Yes.

11:01.835 --> 11:03.619
This is Andy Bouchard here. Uh,
I'm calling about my daughter

11:03.663 --> 11:05.142
Laura. I was just online.

11:05.186 --> 11:07.275
Yes, I was just
about to call your wife.

11:07.318 --> 11:09.103
Why don't you bring
Laura in right now?

11:09.146 --> 11:12.106
That time we discussed,
I think it is now.

11:12.149 --> 11:14.456
What time? Is-- I mean,
is there a problem?

11:14.499 --> 11:15.979
What do these numbers mean?

11:16.023 --> 11:18.329
