the procedure we discussed.

11:22.769 --> 11:23.987
I'll see you
in about 30 minutes.

11:24.031 --> 11:25.336
Wait, wait. What procedure?

11:25.380 --> 11:26.729
Procedure?I think it's best

11:26.773 --> 11:29.297
