in 30 minutes, Mr. Bouchard.

11:29.340 --> 11:30.602
Of course. We'll be right there.

11:30.646 --> 11:31.995
What is it?

11:32.039 --> 11:35.346
Um, where's Laura?

11:35.390 --> 11:36.783
Guys, if you kill someone
who's not a zombie,

11:36.826 --> 11:38.698
then they're gonna
turn into a zombie.Wait, wait.

11:38.741 --> 11:41.744
Is it a running zombie or is it
a slow-walking zombie like...

11:41.788 --> 11:43.267
[babbling]It really doesn't matter.

11:43.311 --> 11:44.573
That's why you have to
shoot them in the legs.

11:44.616 --> 11:45.617
That's how they slow down.

11:45.661 --> 11:47.271
[overlapping shouting]

11:47.315 --> 11:48.620
Quiet, quiet.
Hold on. Quiet, quiet.

11:48.664 --> 11:50.057
We all need to get ready

11:50.100 --> 11:51.406
