to go to the doctor!

11:55.715 --> 11:57.499
And then we're going for i-- and
then we're going for ice cream.

11:57.542 --> 11:58.892
You want ice cream?Yeah! Yeah, yeah!

11:58.935 --> 11:59.936
Okay. So get ready
in ten minutes, please.

11:59.980 --> 12:01.155
Ten minutes. Quickly.

12:01.198 --> 12:03.418
Ten minutes, ten minutes.I love you.

12:03.461 --> 12:05.115
KRISTEN [recorded]:
