12:40.368 --> 12:45.329
Idam guru ratna mandala-kam
nir-yatayami.

12:45.373 --> 12:47.505
Detective, after you
arrested Dwight Ferrell,

12:47.549 --> 12:48.550
what did he tell you?

12:48.593 --> 12:50.508
He said there were more victims.

12:50.552 --> 12:52.336
